text: Wohlen bei Bern is a municipality in the administrative district of Bern- Mittelland in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. It is made of 12 villages: Hinterkappelen, Illiswil, Innerberg, Möriswil, Murzelen, Oberdettigen, Säriswil, Steinisweg, Uettligen, Unterdettigen, Weissenstein and Wickacker. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website of Wohlen bei Bern Category:Municipalities in Bern-Mittelland
title: Wohlen bei Bern
